title: Junga
subTitle: Junga, a simple bus conductor, lives with his mother and learns that his father lost their ancestral property to Chettiyar. However, he soon turns to the life of crime to retrieve it.

title: Aaraattu
subTitle: An affluent man is called upon to hand over his vast plot of land to the government. However, situations take a turn when he brings the influential Neyyattinkara Gopan into the picture.

title: Striker
subTitle: Life changes for Surya, a young boy from Mumbai when he returns home following communal riots. He goes on to become a carrom champion and is pursued by Jaleel, head of a betting syndicate.

title: Rowdy Sardar
subTitle: A young man with a traumatic childhood rises up the ranks to become a dreaded gangster after being a victim of corruption and injustice.

title: Prema Katha Chitram 2
subTitle: After learning that Sudheer is in love with another girl, Bindu commits suicide. However, things take a turn when she returns as a spirit and starts haunting Sudheer and his girlfriend.

title: Kabzaa - The Mafia Raaj
subTitle: Vijay Chandra, a determined police aspirant, battles a local MLA's corrupt efforts to seize his family's land. Joined by other wronged citizens, he takes a stand for justice and honor.

title: Petromax
subTitle: Saravanan, an Indian living abroad, struggles to sell his ancestral home in India due to the supposed presence of ghosts in it. He devises a plan to prove that his house is not haunted.

title: Khatarnak Policewala
subTitle: After a priest's murder and a woman's abduction, ACP Vetrimaaran uncovers a ring linked to a fertility clinic. His investigation takes a personal turn when the conspiracy affects his own family.

title: Baaghi 2
subTitle: Ronny, a soldier, learns of the disappearance of the daughter of his former lover. Soon, his intense investigation leads him to uncover a web of crimes and a secret from the past.

title: MCA: Middle Class Abbayi
subTitle: Nani, a middle-class boy with an eidetic memory, helps save his sister-in-law from a goon. Meanwhile, he also tries to convince his girlfriend's father to marry her off to him.

title: Mega Star God Father
subTitle: The chief minister's passing wreaks havoc across the state and in his political party. However, a mysterious contender for the post rises to eradicate wrongdoers.

title: Tanhaji: The Unsung Warrior
subTitle: Tanhaji, a Maratha warrior, is Shivaji Maharaj's trusted lieutenant. When the Mughals invade and conquer Kondhana fort, he sets out to reclaim it for his king and country.

title: Return of Hanuman
subTitle: Lord Hanuman reincarnates as Maruti to help Minku, a bullied boy, while addressing challenges of modern life, courage and the importance of protecting nature.

title: Anwar

title: Filler

subTitle: Two photographers, who are employed by a newspaper editor to expose the scandalous activities of the rich, come across corruption by a builder and accidentally photograph a murder.

title: RDX

subTitle: A man with a traumatic past is compelled to encounter an crime boss so that he can rescue his daughter from a health problem.

title: Mirai
subTitle: When a vicious villain sets out to claim nine sacred books that hold the secret to immortality, the guardian of the ninth book ties a happy-go-lucky orphan's destiny to the quest to protect them.

title: Aavesham
subTitle: Three boys move into a hostel to pursue engineering, where they clash with seniors. To get revenge, they befriend a gangster.

title: Bharaate
subTitle: Jagan, a local travel guide, falls in love with Radha, a tourist who visits his city. Though she leaves without saying goodbye, fate conspires to being them together again.

subTitle: A vigilante fights against injustice using his own unique moral code, where he only comes out to play on Saturdays.
